post_text: FYI!
shared_text:
Bob Pankey
April 18, 2017 at 11:08 AM 路

2017-18 Benton High School Football Athletes! The 3rd floor clinic in Franklin Hospital will once again offer sport/school physicals for us for next year! The date will be Tuesday, May 23 beginning at 10 AM and the cost will be $20 cash or check (no insurance billed). For sophomore through senior athletes, you only need a sport physical. For in-coming freshman you will need a SCHOOL PHYSICAL which will also count as a sport physical (let the clinic personnel know which you need). Time slots run through 4 PM and need to be scheduled through me. Here's what you will need to take with you to your appt:

SOPH-SENIOR: A filled out 'physical form' which you can obtain from me and your $20 cash or check.

FRESH: A filled out 'physical form' which you can obtain from me, your $20 cash or check and your shot record.

We are very thankful to Franklin Hospital for offering this tremendous service! I encourage you to take advantage of it!!
text:
FYI!

Bob Pankey
April 18, 2017 at 11:08 AM 路

2017-18 Benton High School Football Athletes! The 3rd floor clinic in Franklin Hospital will once again offer sport/school physicals for us for next year! For in-coming freshman you will need a SCHOOL PHYSICAL which will also count as a sport physical (let the clinic personnel know which you need). Time slots run through 4 PM and need to be scheduled through me. Here's what you will need to take with you to your appt:

SOPH-SENIOR: A filled out 'physical form' which you can obtain from me and your $20 cash or check.

FRESH: A filled out 'physical form' which you can obtain from me, your $20 cash or check and your shot record.

We are very thankful to Franklin Hospital for offering this tremendous service! I encourage you to take advantage of it!!
